imdb.title: SPY×FAMILY
imdb.plot: A spy on an undercover mission gets married and adopts a child as part of his cover. His wife and daughter have secrets of their own, and all three must strive to keep together.

episodes.title: Operation Strix
episodes.plot: A spy with the new identity of Loid Forger must find and adopt a child for his next mission.

episodes.title: Secure a Wife
episodes.plot: In need of a wife for the school interview, Twilight crosses with a woman who might be the right cover-up for his mission. She has secrets of her own, though.

episodes.title: Prepare for the Interview
episodes.plot: To prepare for the interview, Loid, Yor and Anya set out for a day in the town, visiting various locations to prepare to sell the image of being a normal upscale family.

episodes.title: The Prestigious School's Interview
episodes.plot: The Forger family goes to Eden School for the interview, where different challenges spice things up, along with the interview itself.

episodes.title: Will They Pass or Fail?
episodes.plot: Anya gets excited about passing the entrance exam but wants some motivation to study, so the family and Franky go on a role play in a castle upon Anya's request.

episodes.title: The Friendship Scheme
episodes.plot: Anya and Yor pick up Anya's school uniform. Later, Anya has her orientation day at Eden Academy, where Loid's Plan B to get close to Donovan via having her befriend his second son, Damien, is off on a disastrous start.

episodes.title: The Target's Second Son
episodes.plot: On Anya's first day of school, Loid attempts to get her to apologize to Damien in hopes of salvaging the plan for the two to become friends. Unfortunately, Damien's conflicting feelings for Anya may get in the way of this.

episodes.title: The Counter-Secret Police Cover Operation
episodes.plot: Yor's younger brother Yuri is a member of the Ostanian Secret Police, hunting spies while keeping it a secret. But when he shows up at the Forgers' residence, their secrets come face to face.

episodes.title: Show Off How In Love You Are
episodes.plot: After Yuri's visit, Loid begins to suspect Yor may not be who she claims. While Loid investigates, Yor struggles with questions of her own.

episodes.title: The Great Dodgeball Plan
episodes.plot: A rumor spreads among the first graders that if they do well in PE, they will be rewarded with Stella Stars. Anya is determined to get one, so she trains with Yor. Thus begins the dodgeball match between Cecile Hall and Wald Hall.

episodes.title: Stella
episodes.plot: In order for parents to attend one of the social gatherings at Eden College, their children must be Imperial Scholars. Anya hates studying, so Loid comes up with a plan for her to get Stella Stars by doing community service.

episodes.title: Penguin Park
episodes.plot: A trip to the local aquarium results in mayhem for the entire Forger family as Loid is assigned a mission that is, fortuitously, located in the same place.

episodes.title: Project Apple
episodes.plot: The thin veneer of peace between Ostania and Westalis threatens to break when terrorists plot an assassination attempt. The Forger family is thrown into the mayhem when searching a for a dog to adopt.

episodes.title: Disarm the Time Bomb
episodes.plot: Anya is saved by your from the terrorists she doesn't know. The intelligent dog sees future which makes the disarming of bomb very important for anya.

episodes.title: A New Family Member
episodes.plot: After being rescued by Anya and a terrorist trained dog, Loid welcomes a new member to the family, Bond, their new pet.

episodes.title: Yor's Kitchen/The Informant's Great Romance Plan
episodes.plot: Believing Loid may start to see her as useless, Yor asks her coworkers to teach her to cook. Franky goes to Loid to help him ask his crush on a date.

episodes.title: Carry Out the Griffin Plan/Fullmetal Lady/Omelet Rice
episodes.plot: Anya attempts to continue the Friendship Plan by helping Damian in arts and crafts, but disastrous results ensue. Sylvia meets with Loid. Yuri toughens up to survive Yor's cooking.

episodes.title: Uncle the Private Tutor/Daybreak
episodes.plot: Yuri helps Anya study for her midterm exams. Afterwards, Loid breaks into Eden Academy's vaults to change her test answers but comes across an amateur spy calling himself Daybreak.

episodes.title: A Revenge Plot Against Desmond/Mama Becomes The Wind
episodes.plot: George, a boy in Anya's class who believes he will be forced to leave Eden, is treated to a luxurious final day of class. Yor dashes to Eden to deliver Anya her gym clothes while Loid tails her.

episodes.title: Investigate the General Hospital/Decipher the Perplexing Code
episodes.plot: Loid takes Anya to the hospital he works at for a school project. Anya spreads a hidden code to her neighbors and classmates. Franky believes a woman may finally be interested in him.

episodes.title: Nightfall/First Fit of Jealousy
episodes.plot: A new spy named Nightfall joins the peacemaking team between East and West. She thinks she can play a better role as Twilight's wife and enters into a mental battle with Yor.

episodes.title: The Underground Tennis Tournament: The Campbelldon
episodes.plot: Twilight and Nightfall enter an underground tennis tournament for a mission as two players and there are no rules in this match and it's a tough match.

episodes.title: The Unwavering Path
episodes.plot: Nightfall and Twilight, who went to a tennis match to get a coded painting, finished their match. After this, Nightfall challenges Yor to a tennis match so that she can take the role of Twilight's wife from her

episodes.title: The Role of a Mother and Wife/Shopping with Friends
episodes.plot: Yur, who thinks that he has been defeated by Nightfall, is upset and sad. Sensing that his mission is in jeopardy, Twilight invites her to a bar to talk about it. Suddenly, something happens to Twilight that hasn't happened in years

episodes.title: First Contact
episodes.plot: With his clever plan, Twilight manages to meet Desmond briefly.
